# Walkthrough: Drive Mapping & Executable Path Fixes

## Fix 1: A: Drive Not Mapped for Any Game

**Root cause:** [XServerScreen.kt](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/xserver/XServerScreen.kt) creates a fresh [ContainerManager](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/container/ContainerManager.java#35-449) from disk, losing in-memory A: drive mapping.

**Fix:** [getContainer()](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/utils/ContainerUtils.kt#L745-L759) now calls [ensureGameDriveMounted()](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/utils/ContainerUtils.kt#653-669) after loading.

## Fix 2: Drives Format Corruption

**Root cause:** [ensureGameDriveMounted()](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/utils/ContainerUtils.kt#653-669) used `split(",")` / `joinToString(",")` to manipulate drives, but the format is concatenated `LETTER:path` with **no commas**. This inserted commas that corrupted other drive paths (E: got a trailing comma).

**Fix:** [ensureGameDriveMounted()](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/utils/ContainerUtils.kt#L704-L720) now uses `Container.drivesIterator()` to properly strip old A: entries and rebuild in the correct format.

## Fix 3: Executable Path Dropdown Blank

**Root cause:** Old comma-corrupted drives strings + forward-slash/backslash display mismatch.

**Fix:** [ExecutablePathDropdown](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/component/dialog/ContainerConfigDialog.kt#L1073-L1096):
- Cleans old comma-corrupted drives via regex before scanning
- Fixed exe filename display to handle forward-slash paths from [scanExecutablesInADrive](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/utils/ContainerUtils.kt#1399-1457)
- Added debug logging for drive mapping and exe scanning

